# vim:set syntax=kconfig:
config CONFIG_ETHTOOL
  bool "ethtool - Ethernet settings tool for PCI ethernet cards"
  default n
  help
    ethtool is a Linux net driver diagnostic and tuning tool for the Linux
    2.4.x (or later) series of kernels. Obtain information and diagnostics
    related to  media, link  status, driver  version, PCI  (or other)  bus
    location, and more.

    http://sourceforge.net/projects/gkernel/
